Package: TLR.zebrafish.stress
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of Toll-Like Receptor Pathway Genes in Zebrafish Stress Models
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Zhixuan", "He", email = "Zhixuan.He22@student.xjtlu.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions to perform Mann-Whitney U tests,
    generate comparison plots of qPCR and RNA-seq results, and produce bubble
    plots of GO enrichment comparing reserpine and chronic stress models in
    zebrafish brain. All data are bundled within the package for reproducible
    analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
    readxl, 
    tidyr,
    reshape2
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
